        {
            "title": "油價飆升,布蘭特原油突破每桶120美元,荷莫茲海峽危機未解",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/u7B5dtyR7bXfVd6kVDGRbg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEB66009_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 油價週四上漲,延續近期漲勢,布蘭特原油一度突破每桶120美元,因美國與伊朗衝突未見進展跡象,<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"荷莫茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:荷莫茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/荷莫茲海峽\">荷莫茲海峽</a>仍未重新開放。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間20:35(北京時間00:35),布蘭特原油期貨上漲1.5%至每桶119.75美元。稍早曾觸及每桶120.34美元,創下2022年6月以來最高水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國WTI原油期貨上漲0.3%至每桶107.25美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本週油價飆升,此前有報導稱美國總統川普正準備對伊朗實施長期海上封鎖。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a8aea7e8-7b21-3e9f-a6ba-e0873b038a16-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">有報導指出,多位美國頂尖石油企業高層在白宮與川普會面,討論如何進一步減輕衝突對美國家庭的影響,這加劇了市場對此類情境的擔憂。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">若實施長期海上封鎖,伊朗很可能繼續封鎖荷莫茲海峽以作報復。該航道若長期受阻,將導致全球石油供應進一步中斷。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自2月底伊朗封鎖該通道以來,經由荷莫茲海峽的船舶運輸幾乎陷入停滯,導致全球約20%的石油供應中斷。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過,週三的一份報導顯示,川普正尋求其他國家協助,組建新的國際聯盟以重新開放該水道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普多次呼籲其他國家協助重新開放荷莫茲海峽,但美國主要盟友大多拒絕提供協助。有報導稱,他對北約成員國在衝突期間未向美國和以色列提供軍事援助表示不滿。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國與伊朗之間的談判因雙方在伊朗核活動問題上存在分歧而基本破裂。儘管川普無限期延長了與伊朗的停火協議,但雙方基本上都拒絕了任何促成談判的嘗試。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿拉伯聯合大公國本週表示將退出石油輸出國組織,油價曾因此短暫停滯。但由於伊朗戰爭造成的干擾,阿聯酋短期內不太可能增加產量。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87-%E5%B8%83%E8%98%AD%E7%89%B9%E5%8E%9F%E6%B2%B9%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4%E6%AF%8F%E6%A1%B6120%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E8%8D%B7%E8%8E%AB%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%AA%E8%A7%A3-020636373.html",
